    </article>

    <article class="Writing__client">
      <div class="Writing__logo">
        <%= image_tag "logos/vode.png", :class => "Image--full Writing__logo--vode", :title => "Vode Lighting", :alt => "Vode Lighting" %>
      </div>
      <div class="Writing__description">
        <p>
          Vode is a Sonoma-based LED and linear lighting design company that needed smart, hip copy for their new blog. It was especially fun to inject humor into the posts, but also explain their innovative technology to the public and drive brand awareness.
        </p>
        <p>
          A lot of upfront research around lighting technology and architecture was poured into this project, and it is still one of the most illuminating (no pun intended) writing experiences I’ve ever had from a professional standpoint because it was both promotional and served as a resource to educate end users.
        </p>
      </div>
