    <article class="Writing__client">
      <div class="Writing__logo">
        <%= image_tag "logos/lost-in-concert.png", :class => "Image--full", :title => "Lost In Concert", :alt => "Lost In Concert" %>
      </div>
      <div class="Writing__description">
        <p>
          Lost in Concert is a blog that tries to encompass the live music experience through photography and words. Having lived in Nashville and Chicago, both huge music towns, I’ve always loved going to shows, so taking on this project for Jimmy Eat World at the Vic Theatre in Chicago was a no-brainer for me.
        </p>
        <p>
          Using words to transport readers to the show was the objective, which I think we definitely achieved here. Not only was it a great concert, but it opened me to the world of music writing which is new medium I love exploring more and more.
        </p>
      </div>
